description: Demolition of Press House building and erection of part 3, 6 and 9 storey building providing 74 residential units (33 x 1bed, 28 x 2bed and 13 x 3bed) with associated car and cycle parking spaces, bin stores, amenity space and landscaping, Subject to a Deed of Agreement dated 27/10/2016 under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990, as amended.
